		<p>Logged in Users may view full-size images as well as edit or delete their own Pins. The public artstream is always handy for viewing on small devices.</p>
		<ol>
			<li>Sign up or Sign in.</li>
			<li>Click on "<b>+ New Pin</b>" in the top bar. Press the "<b>Choose File</b>" button to bring up your computer's finder. Search for the image you want to add. For best results, first reduce large images to 500-700px wide at 72 dpi in your image editor or use the "Save for Web" Photoshop feature. </li>
			<li>Type your description using the keyboard return to break lines of text. Press "<b>Create Pin</b>." </li>
